# Rust
target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock is committed (binary workspace).

# SQLx offline cache — committed so CI can run with SQLX_OFFLINE=true
# (CI does `cargo sqlx prepare --check`, see .github/workflows/ci.yml).
# Regenerate with `cargo sqlx prepare --workspace -- --all-targets`
# against a live Postgres after any SQL change.

